          "date": "2012-05-02 00:05:11.000000000",
          "tz": -420
        },
        "subject": "LU-1027 build: more flexibility for building OFED",
        "message": "LU-1027 build: more flexibility for building OFED\n\nIntroduce new variable to target file\nINFINIBAND={none,inkernel,ofed}\nnone: do not build IB\ninkernel: build using kernel ib driver\nofed: build ofed using OFED_VERSION\n\nWe modify lbuild to support these scenarios\n\n1. if we don't use any --with-ib, --ofed-version\nlbuild will use target file\n2. if we use only --with-ib={none,inkernel,ofed}\nlbuild will build using info provided. In case of\nofed, it will use OFED_VERSION in target file\n3. if we use --ofed-version=x.x.x, lbuild will\nbuild x.x.x and ignore target's file\n\nSigned-off-by: Minh Diep <mdiep@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: I0de8d7a51c442dbd48fdbfe8cb5d00d07b6e8eed\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
  },
